snippet.title: Smol Birb - Visual Novel
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://sonmoss.itch.io/smol-birb?ac=qfCyYFQF Take time to travel along with Zyablik, a small bird who is desperately searching for missing stars.
Will you be kind to everyone who meet along the way or ignore them and their wishes? It`s up to you!
